== Day 1 27.21 ==

[http://events.ccc.de/congress/2005/fahrplan/events/1102.en.html 14:00 room 4: Message generation at the info layer] ([:mp4 :video ftp://dewy.fem.tu-ilmenau.de/CCC/22C3/video/mp4/22C3-1102-en-message_generation_at_the_info_layer.mp4])

How to overcome the communication gap between the information communities and decision makers? After building a simple model on human communication and some introductions we begin to play with message construction learning about how to program the matrix.

